Docs.summary: Run experiment and return the best trial result asynchronizely. The experiment returns the current best trial result if there's any trial completed when get cancelled, and throws with message "Training time finished without completing a trial run" when no trial has completed. Another thing needs to notice is that this function won't immediately return after get cancelled. Instead, it will call to cancel all training process and wait all running trials get cancelled or completed.
